OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBen Wallace: We need to    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finvest in defence properly 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Defence Secretary Ben Wallace has said 
OL,6, the country has to start "investing in 
OL,7, defence properly" as he defended the UK
OL,8, military's readiness for war.          
OL,10,FHe said the army had been "hollowed    
OL,11,Fout" over 30 years and the Ukraine war 
OL,12,Fhad "exposed our vulnerabilities".     
OL,14,FMr Wallace said he wanted a bigger     
OL,15,Fbudget, amid reports he is asking for a
OL,16,F#10bn rise.                            
OL,18,FUK and European officials have raised  
OL,19,Fconcerns over the state of the British 
OL,20,Farmed forces.                          
